Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.72,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Maafkan Bapak, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:18.68,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Setelah ini... lahirlah...\Nke orang tua yang baik-baik...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.29,flashback,Mom,0,0,0,,SAYANG!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.43,flashback,Mom,0,0,0,,Apa yang kamu lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:26.79,flashback,Mom,0,0,0,,Hentikan!\NKalau tak segera berhenti, kutusuk kamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.11,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,LAKUKAN SAJA!\NKALAU KAU PUNYA NYALI!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.86,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Ayo! Coba tusuk aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.09,flashback,Mom,0,0,0,,Hentikan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:41.28,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Kau itu... selalu saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:47.93,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Selalu aja ngebacot...\Ntapi di saat penting... gak ngelakukan apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:54.15,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Selalu... Selalu! Selalu saja!\NKau menganggap dirimu yang paling banyak berjuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:57.02,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Kebanyakan bacot!\NTapi gak bisa apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.01,flashback,Mom,0,0,0,,Henti-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.23,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Sakit, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:07.78,flashback - Red,Dad,0,0,0,,Dibandin rasa sakitku...\NINI BELUM ADA APA-APANYA!
