Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:41.27,sign_Georgia,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs67.5\shad0\bord0\b1\fscx\pos(1626,756)}Bai'at
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:43.93,main,Maki,0,0,0,,Betewe, gue punya kacang cokelat, nih.\NMau makan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.93,0:24:48.22,main,Murasaki,0,0,0,,Gak dulu, deh. Rasanya kalau kumakan itu benda, \Nbisa-bisa otakku ini kenapa-napa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.22,0:24:49.70,main,Maki,0,0,0,,Kalau kacang aja mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.82,0:24:52.73,main,Murasaki,0,0,0,,Rasanya malah makin bahaya, jadi gak dulu.
